        <mxCell id="title-1" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:20px;&quot;&gt;Creación Masiva de Tarjetas (v3 — API Callback Pattern)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;color:#666;&quot;&gt;SFTP / GoAnywhere → S3 → Lambda Validator → Step Functions (Map Distributed) → SQS → ROSA → Callback → Respuesta SFTP&lt;br&gt;✅ taskToken via SQS msg (max 2048 chars) · ✅ SendTaskFailure path · ✅ output ≤ 256KB · ✅ KMS perms · ✅ TaskTimedOut handling · ✅ Dynamic Timeout&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=14;fontColor=#232F3E;" parent="1" vertex="1">
